environment before falling back to test-only output.}

\item{diagram_omit}{Optional character vector of parameter keys or
variable names to omit from the generated SEM path diagram while
retaining them in diagram metadata. Use exact path keys like
\code{"y ~ ideology"} or a variable name like \code{"ideology"} for hidden
covariate-style paths.}

\item{standardized}{Include standardized estimates and standardized-solution
metadata when available.}

\item{tests}{Multivariate test statistics to extract (manova method).
